info.name: pulp-ansible
info.summary: Pulp plugin to manage Ansible content, e.g. roles

vulnerabilities.details: The collection remote for pulp_ansible stores tokens in plaintext instead of using pulp's encrypted field and exposes them in read/write mode via the API () instead of marking it as write only.
